%% Private-tracker authenticated-download path.
%% Constitution V — Private Tracker Bridge Pattern.
%% webui-bridge.py is a host process on :7188, nova2dl.py is a nova3 runtime shim.
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant WebUI as qBittorrent WebUI (:7185)
    participant QB as qBittorrent core
    participant Bridge as webui-bridge.py (:7188 on host)
    participant Nova as nova2dl.py (engines/)
    participant Plugin as private plugin (rutracker/kinozal/nnmclub/iptorrents)
    participant Tracker as Private tracker (HTTPS)
    participant Tmp as ./tmp (shared-tmp bind)

    User->>WebUI: clicks Download on a private-tracker result
    WebUI->>QB: submit URL (qbt://.. or tracker URL)
    QB->>Nova: python3 nova2dl.py <engine> <url>
    Nova->>Plugin: import engines.<name>; <name>().download_torrent(url)
    Plugin->>Bridge: HTTP GET :7188/download?url=...&tracker=<name>
    note over Bridge: reads creds from env / .env / ~/.qbit.env
    Bridge->>Tracker: POST /login (if session absent)
    Tracker-->>Bridge: Set-Cookie: session=<uid>
    Bridge->>Tracker: GET <url> with cookie + Referer
    alt redirect / HTML wrapper
        Tracker-->>Bridge: 302 → /download.php?id=N
        Bridge->>Tracker: GET /download.php?id=N
        Tracker-->>Bridge: application/x-bittorrent
    else direct torrent
        Tracker-->>Bridge: application/x-bittorrent
    end
    Bridge->>Tmp: write /shared-tmp/<uuid>.torrent
    Bridge-->>Plugin: 200 OK, body = torrent bytes
    Plugin-->>Nova: writes magnet or path to stdout
    Nova-->>QB: returns magnet or file path
    QB->>Tmp: reads /shared-tmp/<uuid>.torrent (shared volume)
    QB->>User: torrent queued in qBittorrent
